text: Bella Hadid Goes Punk and Shows Major Underboob In Sheer Shirt During London Fashion Week by Lynda Brendish 3:30 PM PST, February 19, 2017 Playing Bella Hadid Goes Punk and Shows Major Underboob In Sheer Shirt During London Fashion Week Bella Hadid took to the streets of London on Saturday, with a little punk spirit and some major underboob. The 20-year-old model is in the English capital for London Fashion Week, where she rocked an all-black leather and fur outfit on the Versus catwalk. WATCH: Bella Hadid Poses Pantsless for Racy 'V Magazine' Photo Shoot Photo: Getty Images After-hours, Hadid's outfit oozed punk rock chic. While dining at Sexy Fish with pal Kendall Jenner, she sported black lace-up pants with a sheer black top and nipple pasties, accessorized with a blazer, newsboy cap, boots and round sunglasses. Photo: Getty Images Jenner, 21, also channeling rock nâ€™'roll in a a ripped-up band tee with tight leather pants and an oversized rust-colored coat. Photo: Getty Images Racy outfits are getting to be something of a habit for Hadid. Earlier this month, she was photographed for V Magazine sans pants. See the look in the video below.
